{"tid":39961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"爛臉究竟關唔關夜訓事？","createTime":"2016-12-15T01:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T06:36:51.000Z","uid":5012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"043f7c585699788f8a75fa9ed4a249b4729ee25b","tid":39961,"uid":5012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"事關我一路以來都信有關，<br />\n身邊同學好多夜訓，而即使唔夜訓食熱氣嘢都出事<br />\n<br />\n以及間唔中就有文/人講 凌晨幾點幾點就邊到邊到排毒，所以最好幾點幾點前訓教就最好<br />\n<br />\n但係最近識咗個同事，佢最遲12點就訓，<br />\n平時食晏都唔係咩煎炸嘢，3點3又唔會食<br />\n但爛臉過我<br />\n<br />\n有諗過面油關唔關事但應該唔多<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下<br />\n<br />\n利申：學生時期2點先訓，家陣返工1點鬆d訓同買嘢洗臉比以前好咗<br />\n<br />\n仲有除咗勤洗之外仲有咩方法去痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ba93f829c6e5c2d0469144fe86bd41a32989cb","tid":39961,"uid":16343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:22:11.000Z","msg":"日日夜訓白白淨<br />\n<br />\nbtw你指去暗瘡印?<br />\n勤飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc745bfa38e40c77237e5e1861fbdcdc7cc580f","tid":39961,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:22:29.000Z","msg":"食煙都會爛面"},{"pid":"da4aefb7099fde085231cb350d498d7e7b039b47","tid":39961,"uid":61064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:22:55.000Z","msg":"跑步做下運動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604fee58aada0ce00af4bfebe213d7fee62bfe08","tid":39961,"uid":37718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"唔關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日11點訓都係爛面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe03235865ea54869d2c6b00c66c8a675c6321b","tid":39961,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:27:45.000Z","msg":"Ni"},{"pid":"dabc834f368bcca707f638be87218d70e23157a4","tid":39961,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep